[SHORT DESC]
User is made invulnerable for one turn, then hits the next turn.

[LONG DESC]
<p>User is made invulnerable for one turn, then hits the next turn. Sky Uppercut and Thunder have regular Accuracy and Base Power against a Pokémon in the middle of Fly. The Base Power of Gust and Twister doubles against a Pokémon in the charge up stage of Fly.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/moves/bounce">Bounce</a> is a more powerful, less accurate equivalent.</p>